         LOL...I use to click my spells.  But, my optical mouse sometimes goes haywire.  Also, much more efficient when spell effects are going off and the screen is full of motion to just hit alt + spell_gem_number to cast spells.  It took a bit of getting used to, but I would never go back to setting up a spell hotkey or clicking on the gem.  I switch out spells too often and do not use the same gem slot for spells all the time.  Also, my hotkeys are used for things like assist keys, CoS, pet commands, etc.  No room for spells.</P><P>I also use ctrl + character for doing things.  I remapped the exit group command cause I was hitting it alot with my fat fingures.</P><P>The interface looks nice.  I did not see where you could mem a whole spell page...they said they would try to get that in at one time.  Would be nice if they put that in.  Notice...each page has 8 slots...so they may do that in the future if it does not get put in at first.</P><P><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=157918" target=new>Ishtarra Gemeinseele </a><BR>Warlock of the Dirty Soul<BR>Uber N00b Extraordinaire<BR>Tunare Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
